{"tid":2022233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解時事台仲有班人，叫破壞既香港法治制度既人做「建制派」？","createTime":"2020-05-18T08:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T08:58:58.000Z","uid":47208,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d035b015862eea40c21b53ce2164de795ade3f6","tid":2022233,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"今日立法會事件，又見到一堆人用「<span style=\"color: orange;\">建制派</span>」<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: orange;\">建制派</span>」其實唔單只係觀感問題，<br />\n潛移默化下，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實自我降低左呢班人對香港制度既禍害</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">而家既泛民，<br />\n先係真正順應大部份民意，<br />\n做緊破而後立既建制行為。</span><br />\n<br />\n相反，針對近日工聯會、民建聯等，<br />\n破壞民主進程、議會規程既行為，<br />\n好多外國記者已經改用「Pro-Beijing Camp」<br />\n難聽D 講，姐係親共派，<br />\n中立持平D講，係「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">親中派</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n由衷希望各大報章正名，<br />\n亦請大家唔好再為呢班禍港之人，<br />\n冠上建制之名<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少呢個動作，<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為每一件微不足道既小事，<br />\n都可以係改變人心，<br />\n壓倒極權既其中一根稻草</span>"},{"pid":"7bf6133ee7c4fc2e1e0b5d3950b7d1f69cebd3e7","tid":2022233,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"c7e4eaaa488ba710bf3d2ff6972a963c988c8812","tid":2022233,"uid":179718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"少數「親中」破壞派"},{"pid":"2050a08cdea2cc11eaee621985898e3919208484","tid":2022233,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7e4eaaa488ba710bf3d2ff6972a963c988c8812","tid":2022233,"uid":179718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"少數「親中」破壞派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"全部形容都正確<br />\n只係怕太長怕入唔到屋"},{"pid":"adcdc406fc300b845ff9e2bf43d61cca4b120595","tid":2022233,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"以後邊個用建制就